# Metaflora Incubus v1

Metaflora Incubus v1 is a compact local text model for programming, repository
work, tool calls, agentic search, and Russian and English writing. The primary
GGUF download is 5–6 GB. A computer with 16 GB of RAM is recommended.

This card is published only after the release artifact, checksums, licence
review, and benchmark report pass the v1 release gates. Values marked
`NOT_MEASURED` must be replaced from signed benchmark artifacts before upload.

